{"tid":754334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"胡師傅之力威健身之Arnold's Gym!","createTime":"2018-07-24T10:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T22:02:32.000Z","uid":140384,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0caa9a619048a1aad497743390f439646fa2f64","tid":754334,"uid":140384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"依個呀驢 比佢個好師傅推左去選香港先生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/180411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F180411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6b239b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後賣過鴨 ，被指以寸嘴博出位<br />\n<br />\n依加再黎個分道揚鑣 開左間叫 Arnold's Gym <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ArnoldsGymHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FArnoldsGymHK%2F&d=Wo%2BZmH1ARRAQph2s%2BgDj69ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=aa980af6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ArnoldsGymHK/</a><br />\n<br />\n入面啲片個風格似足力威，連條友講野都同胡師傅一鳩樣。 &quot;手藝&quot; &quot;膊頭寬闊&quot; &quot;亞洲人身型&quot;<br />\n<br />\n可以睇翻Fb入面&quot;如何令膊頭寬闊&quot;條片同依條力威嘅教法係一撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/StFk0uzRjYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FStFk0uzRjYo&d=Wo%2BZmH1ARRAQph2s%2BgDj69ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4940f020\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/StFk0uzRjYo</a><br />\n<br />\n又係史密夫機 又係sale亞洲人身型<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，咁點解我仲要去你個gym先？<br />\n<br />\n呀胡師傅同佢講野聽落都唔似學識好高，用詞硬係奇奇怪怪，但佢更差。<br />\n<br />\n佢依條友都真係仆街仔黎，咁樣對自己師傅，仲要不經改良，照版煮碗 <br />\n<br />\n你當我地傻架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63fd9b421e5452607ce6877525c1444d4164cbd","tid":754334,"uid":53503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"佢落曬野操，操到粒奶滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg